		<section id="changelog:basis:univention-python">
			<title>Univention Python</title>
			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem><simpara>
					The &ucsUCRV; <envar>password/quality/mspolicy</envar> has been added to allow
					configuration of standard MS password criteria. It is not active by default.
					When set to <literal>yes</literal> or <literal>true</literal>, this check is applied
					in addition to the <filename>python-cracklib</filename> checks.  If set to
					<literal>sufficient</literal>, then it is done instead of the <filename>python-cracklib</filename>
					checks. See &ucsUCRV; description for details (<u:bug>51994</u:bug>).
				</simpara></listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
		</section>
	</section>

