				<listitem><simpara>
					Proxy settings are now exported as environment variables during the setup (<u:bug>51799</u:bug>).
				</simpara></listitem>
				<listitem><simpara>
					From now on the local unix password for the root account in the UCS appliance images is disabled
					until a proper password is set during the setup (<u:bug>51954</u:bug>). If a ssh login is
					required before the setup, the image has to be modified (e.g. add a ssh key for the root user).
